rows.label: tlk45300157_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This is Shamayim Plant. Entry is forbidden
to all but authorized personnel.

rows.label: tlk45300157_01_msg0002
rows.name:
This plant is where we convert the
heat from inside the Divine Beast into energy
for our steam engines.

rows.label: tlk45300157_01_msg0003
rows.name:
You could call it the foundation of
the Superbian Empire's technology.

rows.label: tlk45300157_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's connected to the plant outside the
city by gondola, but don't you dare
try anything funny, hear?
